            .row.row-grid.mt-5
                .col-lg-4
                    .icon.icon-lg.icon-shape.bg-gradient-white.shadow.rounded-circle.text-primary
                        i.ni.ni-settings.text-primary
                    h5.text-white.mt-3 Promotional tools
                    p.text-white.mt-3
                        | The Facebook builds technologies that give people the power to connect with friends and family, find communities and grow businesses.
                .col-lg-4
                    .icon.icon-lg.icon-shape.bg-gradient-white.shadow.rounded-circle.text-primary
