                    p.text-white.mt-3
                        | Keeping up with friends is faster and easier than ever. Share updates and photos, engage with friends and Pages.
                .col-lg-4
                    .icon.icon-lg.icon-shape.bg-gradient-white.shadow.rounded-circle.text-primary
                        i.ni.ni-atom.text-primary
                    h5.text-white.mt-3 Launch time
                    p.text-white.mt-3
                        | Launching a new product into the market can be the beginning of a wonderful friendshipâ€¦ or a total fiasco.
        // SVG separator
        .separator.separator-bottom.separator-skew.zindex-100
            svg(x='0', y='0', viewBox='0 0 2560 100', preserveAspectRatio='none', version='1.1', xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg')
                polygon.fill-white(points='2560 0 2560 100 0 100')
    section.section.section-lg.pt-lg-0.section-contact-us
        .container
            .row.justify-content-center.mt--300
                .col-lg-8
                    .card.bg-gradient-secondary.shadow
                        .card-body.p-lg-5
                            h4.mb-1 Want to work with us?
                            p.mt-0 Your project is very important to us.
                            .form-group.mt-5
                                .input-group.input-group-alternative
                                    .input-group-prepend
                                        span.input-group-text
                                            i.ni.ni-user-run
                                    input.form-control(placeholder='Your name', type='text')
                            .form-group
                                .input-group.input-group-alternative
                                    .input-group-prepend
                                        span.input-group-text
                                            i.ni.ni-email-83
                                    input.form-control(placeholder='Email address', type='email')
                            .form-group.mb-4
                                textarea.form-control.form-control-alternative(name='name', rows='4', cols='80', placeholder='Type a message...')
                            div
                                button.btn.btn-default.btn-round.btn-block.btn-lg(type='button') Send Message
